sentences: In the 1980s Bernard was a member of the Hieroglyphics Ensemble led by Peter Apfelbaum.
In the 1990s he formed the band T. J. Kirk in San Francisco with Charlie Hunter and John Schott.
Palmetto released his debut solo album, Blue Plate Special, in 2008.
